EXTERNAL COMPONENTS

This product bundles WebRTC (libwebrtc, https://webrtc.googlesource.com/src),
which is available under a "3-clause BSD" license with an additional patent
grant. For details, see licenses/WEBRTC-LICENSE and licenses/WEBRTC-PATENTS
